<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EduCraft LMS - BECE & WASSCE Prep</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=VT323&family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --minecraft-grass: #7CB342;
            --minecraft-dirt: #8B4513;
            --minecraft-stone: #7F8C8D;
            --minecraft-wood: #C19A6B;
            --minecraft-gold: #FFD700;
            --minecraft-diamond: #5DADE2;
            --minecraft-emerald: #00C853;
            --minecraft-redstone: #E53935;
            --minecraft-coal: #37474F;
            --minecraft-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --minecraft-sky: #87CEEB;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--minecraft-sky) 0%, #B8E6F5 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Minecraft pixelated background */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 2px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 4px),
                repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 2px, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 4px);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Header / Navigation */
        .minecraft-header {
            background: var(--minecraft-wood);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dirt);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--minecraft-gold);
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .user-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .stat-item {
            background: var(--minecraft-stone);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--minecraft-gold);
            border: 2px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Navigation Tabs */
        .nav-tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .nav-tab {
            background: var(--minecraft-grass);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            transition: transform 0.1s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .nav-tab:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .nav-tab:active {
            transform: translateY(2px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .nav-tab.active {
            background: var(--minecraft-gold);
            transform: translateY(2px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        /* Page Content */
        .page-content {
            display: none;
        }

        .page-content.active {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Dashboard Grid */
        .dashboard-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .minecraft-card {
            background: var(--minecraft-wood);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .card-header {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--minecraft-gold);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .card-content {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Progress Bars */
        .progress-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .progress-label {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 30px;
            background: var(--minecraft-dark);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--minecraft-emerald);
            transition: width 0.5s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        /* Achievement Cards */
        .achievements-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .achievement {
            background: var(--minecraft-stone);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .achievement:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .achievement.locked {
            opacity: 0.5;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
        }

        .achievement-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin: 0 auto 10px;
            background: var(--minecraft-gold);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        .achievement.locked .achievement-icon {
            background: var(--minecraft-coal);
        }

        /* Lesson Cards */
        .lessons-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .lesson-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--minecraft-wood) 0%, var(--minecraft-dirt) 100%);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            position: relative;
        }

        .lesson-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .lesson-difficulty {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            background: var(--minecraft-redstone);
            border: 2px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 5px 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
        }

        .lesson-title {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--minecraft-gold);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .lesson-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .lesson-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Essay Submission Form */
        .essay-form {
            background: var(--minecraft-wood);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--minecraft-gold);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .form-input,
        .form-textarea,
        .form-select {
            width: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 12px;
            font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .form-textarea {
            min-height: 200px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .form-button {
            background: var(--minecraft-emerald);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            transition: transform 0.1s;
        }

        .form-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .form-button:active {
            transform: translateY(2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        /* File Upload Area */
        .file-upload {
            border: 4px dashed var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .file-upload:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        /* Practice Quiz */
        .quiz-container {
            background: var(--minecraft-wood);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .quiz-question {
            background: var(--minecraft-stone);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .quiz-options {
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .quiz-option {
            background: #fff;
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            color: var(--minecraft-dark);
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .quiz-option:hover {
            background: var(--minecraft-gold);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .quiz-option.selected {
            background: var(--minecraft-diamond);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .quiz-option.correct {
            background: var(--minecraft-emerald);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .quiz-option.incorrect {
            background: var(--minecraft-redstone);
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Leaderboard */
        .leaderboard {
            background: var(--minecraft-wood);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .leaderboard-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .leaderboard-item:nth-child(1) {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--minecraft-gold) 0%, var(--minecraft-wood) 100%);
        }

        .leaderboard-item:nth-child(2) {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #C0C0C0 0%, var(--minecraft-wood) 100%);
        }

        .leaderboard-item:nth-child(3) {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #CD7F32 0%, var(--minecraft-wood) 100%);
        }

        .leaderboard-rank {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 24px;
            min-width: 50px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .leaderboard-avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: var(--minecraft-grass);
            border: 3px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .leaderboard-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .leaderboard-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .leaderboard-score {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--minecraft-gold);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        /* Study Timer */
        .timer-display {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: var(--minecraft-stone);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
        }

        .timer-time {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            font-size: 64px;
            color: var(--minecraft-gold);
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .timer-controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .logo {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .nav-tab {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 10px 16px;
            }

            .timer-time {
                font-size: 42px;
            }

            .card-header {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }

        /* Notification Toast */
        .notification {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: var(--minecraft-emerald);
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            z-index: 1000;
            animation: slideIn 0.3s;
            max-width: 300px;
            display: none;
        }

        .notification.show {
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                transform: translateX(400px);
            }
            to {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        /* Image Gallery */
        .image-gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            border: 4px solid var(--minecraft-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--minecraft-dark);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="minecraft-header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="logo">EDUCRAFT LMS</div>
                <div class="user-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-icon">⭐</div>
                        <span>Level 12</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-icon">💎</div>
                        <span>2,450 XP</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-icon">🔥</div>
                        <span>7 Day Streak</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="nav-tabs">
                <div class="nav-tab active" onclick="showPage('dashboard')">Dashboard</div>
                <div class="nav-tab" onclick="showPage('lessons')">Lessons</div>
                <div class="nav-tab" onclick="showPage('essay')">Essay Portal</div>
                <div class="nav-tab" onclick="showPage('practice')">Practice</div>
                <div class="nav-tab" onclick="showPage('progress')">Progress</div>
                <div class="nav-tab" onclick="showPage('leaderboard')">Leaderboard</div>
                <div class="nav-tab" onclick="showPage('community')">Community</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dashboard Page -->
        <div id="dashboard" class="page-content active">
            <div class="dashboard-grid">
                <div class="minecraft-card">
                    <div class="card-header">Welcome Back, Student!</div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>You're preparing for BECE & WASSCE exams. Keep up the great work!</p>
                        <br>
                        <p>🎯 Today's Goal: Complete 3 lessons</p>
                        <p>📚 Current Focus: Essay Writing</p>
                        <p>⏰ Study Time Today: 45 minutes</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="minecraft-card">
                    <div class="card-header">Quick Stats</div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <div class="progress-item">
                            <div class="progress-label">
                                <span>BECE Prep</span>
                                <span>68%</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="progress-bar">
                                <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 68%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-item">
                            <div class="progress-label">
                                <span>WASSCE Prep</span>
                                <span>45%</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="progress-bar">
                                <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 45%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="progress-item">
                            <div class="progress-label">
                                <span>Essay Writing</span>
                                <span>82%</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="progress-bar">
                                <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 82%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="minecraft-card">
                    <div class="card-header">Recent Achievements</div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <div class="achievements-grid">
                            <div class="achievement">
                                <div class="achievement-icon">🏆</div>
                                <div>First Essay</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="achievement">
                                <div class="achievement-icon">📖</div>
                                <div>Bookworm</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="achievement">
                                <div class="achievement-icon">⚡</div>
                                <div>Speed Reader</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="achievement locked">
                                <div class="achievement-icon">👑</div>
                                <div>Master</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="minecraft-card">
                <div class="card-header">Continue Learning</div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="lessons-grid">
                        <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson started!')">
                            <div class="lesson-difficulty">EASY</div>
                            <div class="lesson-title">Essay Structure</div>
                            <div class="lesson-description">Learn the fundamentals of essay writing including introduction, body, and conclusion.</div>
                            <div class="lesson-stats">
                                <span>⏱️ 15 min</span>
                                <span>⭐ 100 XP</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson started!')">
                            <div class="lesson-difficulty">MEDIUM</div>
                            <div class="lesson-title">IE & EI Words</div>
                            <div class="lesson-description">Master tricky spelling with 'I before E except after C' rule and exceptions.</div>
                            <div class="lesson-stats">
                                <span>⏱️ 20 min</span>
                                <span>⭐ 150 XP</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson started!')">
                            <div class="lesson-difficulty">HARD</div>
                            <div class="lesson-title">Narrative Composition</div>
                            <div class="lesson-description">Write compelling narratives with proper character development and plot structure.</div>
                            <div class="lesson-stats">
                                <span>⏱️ 30 min</span>
                                <span>⭐ 250 XP</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Lessons Page -->
        <div id="lessons" class="page-content">
            <div class="minecraft-card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="card-header">BECE & WASSCE Curriculum</div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p>Comprehensive lessons covering all exam topics with interactive exercises and gamified learning.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="lessons-grid">
                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Essay Writing started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">EASY</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Essay Writing Basics</div>
                    <div class="lesson-description">Understanding essay structure, thesis statements, and paragraph organization.</div>
                    <div class="lesson-stats">
                        <span>⏱️ 15 min</span>
                        <span>⭐ 100 XP</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Spelling started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">EASY</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Tricky Spelling</div>
                    <div class="lesson-description">Master IE/EI words, common mistakes, and spelling rules with interactive practice.</div>
                    <div class="lesson-stats">
                        <span>⏱️ 20 min</span>
                        <span>⭐ 120 XP</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Narrative started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">MEDIUM</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Narrative Composition</div>
                    <div class="lesson-description">Create engaging stories with proper plot structure, dialogue, and descriptive writing.</div>
                    <div class="lesson-stats">
                        <span>⏱️ 25 min</span>
                        <span>⭐ 180 XP</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Argumentative started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">MEDIUM</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Writing to Argue</div>
                    <div class="lesson-description">Develop persuasive arguments with evidence, counterarguments, and logical structure.</div>
                    <div class="lesson-stats">
                        <span>⏱️ 30 min</span>
                        <span>⭐ 200 XP</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Newspaper started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">HARD</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Newspaper Articles</div>
                    <div class="lesson-description">Write journalistic pieces with headlines, lead paragraphs, and inverted pyramid structure.</div>
                    <div class="lesson-stats">
                        <span>⏱️ 35 min</span>
                        <span>⭐ 250 XP</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Grammar started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">MEDIUM</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Grammar Mastery</div>
                    <div class="lesson-description">Perfect your grammar skills with tenses, subject-verb agreement, and punctuation.</div>
                    <div class="lesson-stats">
                        <span>⏱️ 40 min</span>
                        <span>⭐ 220 XP</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lesson-card" onclick="showNotification('Lesson: Vocabulary started!')">
                    <div class="lesson-difficulty">EASY</div>
                    <div class="lesson-title">Vocabulary Building</div>
